msgctxt "84_Scared Businesswoman"
msgid "What's going on? I hope it's not dangerous..."
msgstr "¿Qué está pasando? Ojalá que no sea nada grave..."

msgctxt "96_Confident Businesswoman"
msgid "You'll be fine. I mean, just look at how many cops are\r\n"
"around."
msgstr "Tranquila, estarás bien. Mira la cantidad de policías\r\n"
"que hay por ahí."

